snippet.title: #therapists view on the #princessdiana statue, #princeharry behaviour & #amberheard. 🤔
snippet.description:
Hey Bubble Family 

Well It’s just me this week as licky Taz is getting prepared for her holibob 😃
I’m not jealous at all 😂😂

So I thought I’d give my take on a few things regarding 
Merchie & Lili 
The Diana Statue 
Amber Turds new baby 

Plus a little surprise video at the end! 

I hope you continue to support the videos I do on my little ole lonesome
